			<b>ctrl+shift+c:</b> Åpne/lukke HTML-kode</p>
			<hr>
			<h3 class="headerSmall">Målet</h3>
			<p>Målet med å lage et levende desigsystem er:
				<ul>
					<li>Maintain a consistency of styles and identity in all Alltinn's web solutions</li>
					<li>Having one common prototype environment where we are simultaneously able to see components abstractly and in context</li>
					<li>Streamline the workflow for designers and developers</li>
					<li>Create a focal point for our Design and User Experience work, both for ourselves and for the community</li>
				</ul>


				<h3 class="headerSmall">Rutiner for oppdatering</h3>
